'''Baselios Sakralla 3rd of Aleppo''' was the Maphriyano (Catholicos) of the [[Syriac Orthodox Church]] of the East from 1748-1760.
Maphriyano Sakralla came to India in 1751 and was buried at [[Kandanad]] Martha Mariyam Church in 1764 AD.
He was declared a Saint by the [[Patriarch]] of the [[Syriac Orthodox Church]] in 2008.
