'''Bharatiya Girvana Prouda Vidya Vardhini Shala''' is an institution and seminary of higher learning in [[Sanskrit]], [[Vedanta]], [[Mimamsa]], literature and other allied subjects located in the premises of the Shankara [[Matha]] in Shankarapuram, [[Basavanagudi]], [[Bangalore]]. It was inaugurated by [[Sacchidananda Shivabhinava Narasimha Bharati|Sri Sachhidananda Shivabhinava Narasimha Bharati Swaminah]], the then Jagadguru of the [[Sringeri Sharada Peetham]] in 1910.

